{"id":35,"parent_id":31,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":35,"title":"Mark 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mark","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus gives the parables of the sower, the candle under a bushel, the seed growing secretly, and the mustard seed—He stills the tempest."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.1","order":"03.04.004.4308"},["b","1"],"And he began again to teach by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"sea"],"side: and there was gathered unto him a great multitude, so that he entered into a ship, and sat in the sea; and the whole multitude was by the sea on the land."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.2","order":"03.04.004.4309"},["b","2"],"And he taught them many things by parables, and said unto them in his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"doctrine"],","],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.3","order":"03.04.004.4310"},["b","3"],"Hearken; Behold, there went out a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sower"],"to sow:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.4","order":"03.04.004.4311"},["b","4"],"And it came to pass, as he sowed, some fell by the way side, and the fowls of the air came and devoured it up."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.5","order":"03.04.004.4312"},["b","5"],"And some fell on stony ground, where it had not much earth; and immediately it sprang up, because it had no depth of earth:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.6","order":"03.04.004.4313"},["b","6"],"But when the sun was up, it was scorched; and because it had no root, it withered away."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.7","order":"03.04.004.4314"},["b","7"],"And some fell among thorns, and the thorns grew up, and choked it, and it yielded no fruit."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.8","order":"03.04.004.4315"},["b","8"],"And other fell on good ground, and did yield fruit that sprang up and increased; and brought forth, some thirty, and some sixty, and some an hundred."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.9","order":"03.04.004.4316"},["b","9"],"And he said unto them, He that hath ears to hear, let him hear."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.10","order":"03.04.004.4317"},["b","10"],"And when he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"alone, they that were"],"about him with the twelve asked of him the parable."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.11","order":"03.04.004.4318"},["b","11"],"And he said unto them, Unto you it is given to know the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"mystery"],"of the kingdom of God: but unto them that are without, all",["i","these"],"things are done in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"parables"],":"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.12","order":"03.04.004.4319"},["b","12"],"That seeing they may see, and not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"perceive"],"; and hearing they may hear, and not understand; lest at any time they should be converted, and",["i","their"],"sins should be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"forgiven"],"them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.13","order":"03.04.004.4320"},["b","13"],"And he said unto them, Know ye not this parable? and how then will ye know all parables?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.14","order":"03.04.004.4321"},["b","14"],"¶The sower soweth the word."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.15","order":"03.04.004.4322"},["b","15"],"And these are they by the way side, where the word is sown; but when they have heard,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Satan"],"cometh immediately, and taketh away the word that was sown in their hearts."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.16","order":"03.04.004.4323"},["b","16"],"And these are they likewise which are sown on stony ground; who, when they have heard the word, immediately",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"receive"],"it with gladness;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.17","order":"03.04.004.4324"},["b","17"],"And have no root in themselves, and so endure but for a time: afterward, when",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"affliction"],"or",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"persecution"],"ariseth for the word’s sake, immediately they are offended."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.18","order":"03.04.004.4325"},["b","18"],"And these are they which are sown among thorns; such as hear the word,"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.19","order":"03.04.004.4326"},["b","19"],"And the cares of this world, and the deceitfulness of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"riches"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"lusts"],"of other things entering in, choke the word, and it becometh unfruitful."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.20","order":"03.04.004.4327"},["b","20"],"And these are they which are sown on good ground; such as hear the word, and receive",["i","it,"],"and bring forth fruit, some thirtyfold, some sixty, and some an hundred."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.21","order":"03.04.004.4328"},["b","21"],"¶And he said unto them, Is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"candle"],"brought to be put under a bushel, or under a bed? and not to be set on a candlestick?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.22","order":"03.04.004.4329"},["b","22"],"For there is nothing hid, which shall not be manifested; neither was any thing kept secret, but that it should come abroad."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.23","order":"03.04.004.4330"},["b","23"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"If"],"any man have ears to hear, let him hear."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.24","order":"03.04.004.4331"},["b","24"],"And he said unto them, Take heed what ye hear: with what measure ye mete, it shall be measured to you:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"and"],"unto you that hear shall more be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"given"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.25","order":"03.04.004.4332"},["b","25"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"For"],"he that hath, to him shall be given: and he that hath not, from him shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"taken"],"even that which he hath."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.26","order":"03.04.004.4333"},["b","26"],"¶And he said, So is the kingdom of God, as if a man should cast seed into the ground;"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.27","order":"03.04.004.4334"},["b","27"],"And should sleep, and rise night and day, and the seed should spring and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"grow up"],", he knoweth not how."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.28","order":"03.04.004.4335"},["b","28"],"For the earth bringeth forth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"fruit"],"of herself; first the blade, then the ear, after that the full corn in the ear."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.29","order":"03.04.004.4336"},["b","29"],"But when the fruit is brought forth, immediately he putteth in the sickle, because the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"harvest"],"is come."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.30","order":"03.04.004.4337"},["b","30"],"¶And he said, Whereunto shall we liken the kingdom of God? or with what comparison shall we compare it?"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.31","order":"03.04.004.4338"},["b","31"],["i","It is"],"like a grain of mustard seed, which, when it is sown in the earth, is less than all the seeds that be in the earth:"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.32","order":"03.04.004.4339"},["b","32"],"But when it is sown, it groweth up, and becometh greater than all herbs, and shooteth out great branches; so that the fowls of the air may lodge under the shadow of it."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.33","order":"03.04.004.4340"},["b","33"],"And with many such parables spake he the word unto them, as they were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"able to hear",["i","it"]],["i","."]],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.34","order":"03.04.004.4341"},["b","34"],"But without a parable spake he not unto them: and when they were alone, he expounded all things to his disciples."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.35","order":"03.04.004.4342"},["b","35"],"And the same day, when the even was come, he saith unto them, Let us pass over unto the other side."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.36","order":"03.04.004.4343"},["b","36"],"And when they had sent away the multitude, they took him even as he was in the ship. And there were also with him other little ships."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.37","order":"03.04.004.4344"},["b","37"],"And there arose a great storm of wind, and the waves beat into the ship, so that it was now full."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.38","order":"03.04.004.4345"},["b","38"],"And he was in the hinder part of the ship, asleep on a pillow: and they awake him, and say unto him, Master, carest thou not that we perish?"],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.39","order":"03.04.004.4346"},["b","39"],"And he arose, and rebuked the wind, and said unto the sea,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"Peace"],", be still. And the wind ceased, and there was a great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"calm"],"."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.40","order":"03.04.004.4347"},["b","40"],"And he said unto them, Why are ye so",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"fearful"],"? how is it that ye have no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_40b"},"faith"],"?"],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.41","order":"03.04.004.4348"},["b","41"],"And they feared exceedingly, and said one to another, What manner of man is this, that even the wind and the sea obey him?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.1a","order":"03.04.004.4349"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.1"},"Matt. 13:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.2a","order":"03.04.004.4351"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.39.31-41"},"3 Ne. 11:39 (31–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.3a","order":"03.04.004.4353"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/86.2.2-3"},"D&C 86:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.10a","order":"03.04.004.4355"},["b","10a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 4:9 … alone",["i","with the twelve, and they that believed in him,"],"they that were …"],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.11a","order":"03.04.004.4357"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"TG Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.11b","order":"03.04.004.4359"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.35.34-35"},"Matt. 13:35 (34–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/8.10"},"Luke 8:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-teaching-mode-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Teaching Mode of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.12a","order":"03.04.004.4361"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.12b","order":"03.04.004.4363"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.15a","order":"03.04.004.4365"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.16a","order":"03.04.004.4367"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/40.2"},"D&C 40:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.17a","order":"03.04.004.4369"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/8.28.24-28"},"1 Ne. 8:28 (24–28)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.17b","order":"03.04.004.4371"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.19a","order":"03.04.004.4373"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.19b","order":"03.04.004.4375"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.21a","order":"03.04.004.4377"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.24"},"3 Ne. 18:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.23a","order":"03.04.004.4379"},["b","23a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-isa/42.19-23"},["span.small","JST"],"Isa. 42:19–23 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.24a","order":"03.04.004.4381"},["b","24a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 4:20 … and unto you that",["i","continue to receive,"],"shall more be given …"],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.24b","order":"03.04.004.4383"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/25.15"},"Matt. 25:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/8.18"},"Luke 8:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.25a","order":"03.04.004.4385"},["b","25a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 4:20 … for he that",["i","receiveth,"],"to him shall be given;",["i","but"],"he that",["i","continueth not to receive,"],"from him shall …"],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.25b","order":"03.04.004.4387"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.10"},"D&C 43:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/60.3"},"60:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.27a","order":"03.04.004.4389"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.6.6-7"},"1 Cor. 3:6 (6–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.28a","order":"03.04.004.4391"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/nature-earth"},"TG Nature, Earth"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.29a","order":"03.04.004.4393"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/harvest"},"TG Harvest"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.33a","order":"03.04.004.4395"},["b","33a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 4:26 … able to",["i","bear;"],"but without …"],["div",{"id":"39a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.39a","order":"03.04.004.4397"},["b","39a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace"},"TG Peace"],"."],["div",{"id":"39b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.39b","order":"03.04.004.4399"},["b","39b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.9"},"Ps. 89:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.40a","order":"03.04.004.4401"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/14.31"},"Matt. 14:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/16.14"},"Mark 16:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/24.25"},"Luke 24:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"40b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/4.40b","order":"03.04.004.4403"},["b","40b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/44.4.1-5"},"Alma 44:4 (1–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/4.5.1-7"},"D&C 4:5 (1–7)"],"."]]}
